                "→ Chọn đáp án C",
                "*\nRead the following leaflet and mark the letter A, B, C or D on your answer sheet to indicate the option that best fits each of the numbered blanks from 35 to 40.*",
                "EXPLORE CULTURAL DIVERSITY",
