                "c. My favorite place was Gyeongbokgung Palace, which was spectacular and famous for its architecture.",
                "d. The following morning, my dad likes visiting historical sites, so we went to some ancient palaces.\ne. We really enjoyed the breathtaking city view from our room.",
                "A. b-a-e-d-c",
