                "###\nQuestion 3.",
                "Hi Sarah,",
                "1. It's so exciting to try something new, but I've been really busy with my photography class recently.\n2. Thanks so much for recommending those painting tutorial videos last week!\n3. Maybe we could work on a creative project together sometime. What do you think?\n4. Also, the website you suggested for free art classes is incredible way better than the ones I've used before.\n5. I haven't started painting yet, but I've watched a few videos, and they're super inspiring.",
